<section id="lucky-numbers">
  <h2>Lucky Numbers for 2026</h2>
  <p>The assignment of numbers to elements follows the <strong>Hetu</strong> (<span class="chinese-char">河圖</span>, River Map) system, one of the foundational diagrams of Chinese cosmology. The <em>Xici Zhuan</em> (<span class="chinese-char">繫辭傳</span>, Commentary on the Appended Phrases), a wing of the <em>Yijing</em>, states: "Heaven one generates Water, Earth six completes it; Earth two generates Fire, Heaven seven completes it; Heaven three generates Wood, Earth eight completes it; Earth four generates Metal, Heaven nine completes it; Heaven five generates Earth, Earth ten completes it." This passage establishes the canonical number-element pairs that govern numerical auspiciousness.</p>

