        <td>Earth channels Fire output. Good for study, meditation, and knowledge pursuits. The Gen trigram represents stillness and contemplation.</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Southwest</strong></td>
        <td>Earth</td>
        <td>Kun (<span class="chinese-char">坤</span>)</td>
